ncept","schema_type":"array","effectiveId":"https://cdif.org/0.1/uses_Concept"},{"path":["_anyOf","0","cdif:isDefinedBy_RepresentedVariable","cdi:measures","cdif:uses_Concept","skos:narrower"],"id":"http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#narrower","description":"Narrower (child) concepts in the hierarchy. Items are inline concept objects or @id references.","schema_type":"array","effectiveId":"http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#narrower"},{"path":["_anyOf","0","cdif:isDefinedBy_RepresentedVariable","cdi:measures","cdif:uses_Concept","skos:broader"],"id":"http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#broader","description":"Broader (parent) concepts in the hierarchy. Items are inline concept objects or @id references.","schema_type":"array","effectiveId":"http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#broader"},{"path":["_anyOf","0","cdif:isDefinedBy_RepresentedVariable","cdi:measures","cdif:uses_Concept","skos:topConceptOf"],"id":"http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#topConceptOf","description":"Concept scheme(s) for which this is a top concept.","effectiveId":"http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#topConceptOf"},{"path":["_anyOf","0","cdif:isDefinedBy_RepresentedVariable","cdi:measures","cdif:uses_Concept","skos:inScheme"],"id":"http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#inScheme","description":"Concept scheme(s) this concept belongs to.","required":true,"effectiveId":"http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#inScheme"},{"path":["_anyOf","0","cdif:isDefinedBy_RepresentedVariable","cdi:measures","cdif:uses_Concept","skos:editorialNote"],"id":"http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#editorialNote","description":"Note for editors and maintainers.","effectiveId":"http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#editorialNote"},{"path":["_anyOf","0","cdif:isDefinedBy_RepresentedVariable","cdi:measures","cdif:uses_Concept","skos:changeNote"],"id":"http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#changeNote","description":"Note documenting a change.","effectiveId":"http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#changeNote"},{"path":["_anyOf","0","cd